16:48.050 --> 16:53.534
♪ Endureth forever

16:53.577 --> 16:56.058
♪ People from every
nation and tongue ♪

16:56.102 --> 17:00.280
♪ From generation
to generation ♪

17:00.323 --> 17:02.804
♪ We worship you... Welcome, everyone,

17:02.847 --> 17:04.762
to God's house.

17:04.806 --> 17:07.983
Today's service
will be about love.

17:08.027 --> 17:12.596
Of God and the people
that God has put into our lives.

17:12.640 --> 17:15.947
I firmly believe that
He sends us certain people

17:15.991 --> 17:18.559
at the precise moment
we need them.

17:18.602 --> 17:20.387
Perhaps it is
to bring us

17:20.430 --> 17:25.305
perspective, appreciation.

17:25.348 --> 17:29.265
Or perhaps it is just
to remind us that we are human.

17:29.309 --> 17:30.788
And though we are not perfect...

17:32.225 --> 17:34.488
...it is within
those imperfections

17:34.531 --> 17:36.403
that we find
connection.

17:37.621 --> 17:39.754
And what could be more perfect

17:39.797 --> 17:41.756
than connecting
with another soul...

17:43.149 --> 17:45.281
...and showing God
the joy

17:45.325 --> 17:47.936
of His creation?

