Check the inside pocket.

18:09.044 --> 18:10.132
That's two tickets

18:10.176 --> 18:11.394
to the Lions home opener.

18:11.438 --> 18:12.961
You and I are gonna
watch them start

18:13.004 --> 18:15.616
their championship season
in person.

18:15.659 --> 18:16.834
That is very nice.

18:16.878 --> 18:20.142
And again, I'm sorry.

18:20.186 --> 18:23.363
Okay? Next year, I promise,
you're getting that bonus.

18:23.406 --> 18:24.625
If you say so.

18:24.668 --> 18:26.322
All right, I'll see you soon.

18:26.366 --> 18:27.845
Goodbye, Mr. Wheeler.

18:28.803 --> 18:30.370
We're all set.

18:30.413 --> 18:32.937
The rest of the team's
ready to meet you.

18:32.981 --> 18:34.939
I appreciate you
getting me this interview.

18:34.983 --> 18:38.117
Oh, are you kidding?
They are gonna love you.

18:38.160 --> 18:39.857
This is the right move, Goodwin.

18:39.901 --> 18:41.250
Yes, it is.

18:43.600 --> 18:44.993
Love that jacket.

